-giant-noorjahan-mangoes-india-shivraj-singh-jadav-mango-farming-guide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efew%20mangoes%20to%20survive%20on%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20farmers%20by%20choice%20but%20by%20necessity.%20Back%20then%2C%20it%20was%20just%20about%20growing%20enough%20to%20eat%20and%20sell%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20next%20day%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20harder%20than%20the%20one%20before.%20But%20from%20that%20simple%20start%2C%20something%20incredible%20grew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20A%20Jayapal%20is%20in%20his%20orchard%2C%20his%20hands%20stained%20yellow%20from%20the%20mangoes%20he%E2%80%99s%20carefully%20sorting%20and%20packing.%20The%20air%20is%20thick%20with%20heat%2C%20and%20the%20scent%20of%20ripening%20fruit%20fills%20the%20space%20around%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayapal%E2%80%99s%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20follow%20the%20usual%20story%20of%20climbing%20corporate%20ladders%20or%20seeking%20fortune%20in%20cities.%20They%20stayed%20grounded%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20with%20their%20hands%20in%20the%20soil.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20struggle%20to%20survive%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20legacy%20built%20around%20one%20fruit%20they%E2%80%99ve%20always%20loved%3A%20the%20mango.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Jayapals%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20never%20been%20about%20the%20quick%20win.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20steady%20work%2C%20dedication%2C%20and%20passion%20%E2%80%94%20traits%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20this%20family%20has%20gone%20from%20scraping%20by%20to%20becoming%20a%20name%20known%20for%20their%20quality%20mangoes.%20And%20through%20it%20all%2C%20that%20love%20for%20the%20mango%2C%20a%20fruit%20that%20once%20me