sury%20Secretary%20Lawrence%20Summers%20told%20Bloomberg%20Television's%20Wall%20Street%20Week%20that%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Battack%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20IRS%20could%20cost%20the%20government%20%241%20trillion.%3Cp%3ERob%20Kim%2FGetty%20Images%20and%20Andrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEx-Treasury%20Secretary%20Larry%20Summers%20said%20Trump's%20IRS%20cuts%20could%20cost%20the%20government%20%241%20trillion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Yale%20economist%20told%20BI%20that%20his%20estimate%20is%20conservative%2C%20and%20actual%20losses%20could%20top%20%242%20trillion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20has%20ordered%20sweeping%20cuts%20at%20the%20IRS%20to%20increase%20%26quot%3Befficiency%20and%20effectiveness%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20former%20Treasury%20Secretary%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-summers-us-economy-donald-trump-tariffs-stocks-bonds-gold-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELawrence%20Summers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0said%20that%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bmisguided%2C%20wanton%20attack%20on%20the%20IRS%26quot%3B%20could%20cost%20the%20government%20%241%20trillion%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20aggressive%20cost-cutting%20strategy%2C%20Trump%20has%20ordered%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firs-offers-deferred-resignation-buyouts-to-employees-reduction-in-force-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweeping%20cuts%20at%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20increase%20the%20agency's%20%26quot%3Befficiency%20and%20effectiveness.%26quot%3B%20These%20layoffs%20include%20a%2075%25%20reduction%20in%20the%20IRS's%20Office%20of%20Civil%20Rights%20and%20Compliance%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20investigating%20complaints%20of%20discrimination%20against%20taxpayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statutory%20body%20has%20also%20experienced%20repeated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleadership-shakeups-multiple-different-irs-bosses-tax-week-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleadership%20shake-ups%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20Trump%20took%20office.%20Five%20different%20people%20have%20held%20the%20role%20of%20acting%20commissioner%20since%20January%2C%C2%A0including%20three%20different%20people%20during%20tax%20week%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESummers%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Treasury%20Secretary%20under%20Bill%20Clinton's%20administration%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2F2025-04-22%2Fsummers-sees-raw-incompetence-in-trump-handling-of-irs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg's%3C%2Fa%3E%20David%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWestin%20that%20Trump's%20efforts%20to%20cut%20IRS%20staff%20are%20%26quot%3Bthreatening%20the%20basis%20of%20our%20tax%20system%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20voluntary%20compliance%26quot%3B%20and%20described%20the%20president's%20approach%20in%20leading%20the%20agency%20as%20%26quot%3Braw%20incompetence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20be%20surprised%20if%20we're%20not%20on%20a%20path%20to%20sacrificing%20more%20than%20%241%20trillion%20of%20revenue%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20because%20of%20this%20misguided%2C%20wanton%20attack%20on%20the%20IRS%2C%26quot%3B%20Summers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENatasha%20Sarin%2C%20the%20president%20and%20cofounder%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-cost-consumers-thousands-food-clothes-price-increase-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBudget%20Lab%20at%20Yale%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Summers'%20estimate%20is%20conservative%2C%20and%20the%20losses%20may%20top%20%242%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20that%20we%20have%20a%20very%20large%20gap%20in%20this%20country%20between%20taxes%20that%20are%20owed%20and%20taxes%20that%20are%20collected%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarin%20said%2C%20estimating%20that%20this%20year%20there%20will%20be%20about%20%24700%20billion%20in%20taxes%20that%20are%20owed%20but%20won't%20be%20collected%2C%20due%20to%20filers%20failing%20to%20report%20or%20under-reporting%20their%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20intended%20to%20streamline%20IRS%20functions%2C%20Trump's%20cuts%20hamstring%20the%20agency's%20ability%20to%20appropriately%20audit%20the%20nation's%20tax%20filings%20and%2C%20because%20the%20IRS%20is%20responsible%20for%20collecting%20about%2096%25%20of%20the%20total%20federal%20revenue%2C%20may%20prevent%20the%20agency%20from%20collecting%20the%20revenue%20that%20builds%20schools%20and%20roads%20and%20covers%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20our%20defense%20spending%2C%20Sarin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20effect%20that%20happens%20when%20you%20don't%20do%20tax%20enforcement%20is%20kind%20of%20like%20not%20having%20traffic%20cops%20on%20the%20roads%20in%20that%20there's%20a%20direct%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarin%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20fewer%20tickets%20or%20fewer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Ftax-audit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaudits%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20done%2C%20then%20there's%20less%20revenue%20that%20comes%20but%20there's%20also%20this%20really%20important%20behavioral%20effect%3A%20if%20you%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20traffic%20camera%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20obey%20the%20speed%20limit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20same%20thing%20happens%20with%20the%20tax%20code.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbudgetlab.yale.edu%2Fresearch%2Frevenue-and-distributional-effects-irs-funding%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBudget%20Lab%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimated%20that%20if%20the%20IRS%20shrinks%20by%2050%25%20%E2%80%94%20a%20workforce%20decrease%20of%20about%2050%2C000%20people%20%E2%80%94%20the%20losses%20will%20amount%20to%20%24395%20b