%20%E2%80%94%20the%20pair%20of%20superhighways%20in%20your%20neck%20that%20channel%20blood%20to%20your%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20in%20plastic%20quantities%20surprised%20him%2C%20but%20his%20team%20found%20another%20concerning%20trend%2C%20too.%20Cells%20in%20the%20plaque%20with%20lots%20of%20plastic%20showed%20different%20gene%20activity%20than%20those%20with%20low%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20high-plastic%20environment%2C%20one%20group%20of%20immune%20cells%20had%20switched%20off%20a%20gene%20that's%20associated%20with%20turning%20off%20inflammation.%20Clark's%20team%20also%20found%20genetic%20differences%20in%20a%20group%20of%20stem%20cells%20thought%20to%20help%20prevent%20heart%20attacks%20and%20strokes%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplement-scientist-heart-health-inflammation-daily-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereducing%20inflammation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20stabilizing%20plaque.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCould%20it%20be%20that%20microplastics%20are%20somehow%20altering%20their%20gene%20expression%3F%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20there's%20%26quot%3Blots%20more%20research%20needed%20to%20fully%20establish%20that%2C%20but%20at%20least%20it%20gives%20us%20a%20hint%20as%20to%20where%20to%20look.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%2C%20who%20specializes%20in%20the%20genetic%20mechanisms%20behind%20disease%2C%20agreed%20that%20more%20research%20is%20needed%2C%20but%20added%20that%20she%20thinks%20%26quot%3Bthese%20plastics%20are%20doing%20something%20with%20these%20plaques.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227049dfc4-c891-4a1f-9760-e8ce1a0993dc%5C%22%3E'We%20just%20don't%20know'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETracking%20microplastics%20in%20the%20human%20body%20is%20a%20new%20scientific%20endeavor%20as%20of%20the%20last%20couple%20years.%20It's%20not%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark's%20team%20heated%20the%20plaque%20samples%20to%20more%20than%201%2C000%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20to%20vaporize%20plastic%20polymers%20and%20break%20them%20down%20into%20smaller%20organic%20molecules%2C%20which%20can%20be%20identified%20and%20measured%20by%20their%20mass%20and%20other%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20lipids%20in%20plaque%20can%20break%20down%20into%20chemicals%20that%20look%20very%20similar%20to%20polyethylene%2C%20the%20most%20common%20plastic%20found%20in%20everything%20from%20plastic%20bags%20to%20car%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20know%20about%20this%20problem%2C%20we've%20taken%20a%20lot%20of%20steps%20to%20remove%20those%20lipids%20and%20confirm%20their%20removal%2C%20so%20that%20we're%20sure%20we're%20measuring%20polyethylene%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20a%20big%20limitation%2C%20and%20it%20should%20be%20acknowledged%20that%20these%20types%20of%20methodologies%20are%20continuously%20improving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20funding%20to%20further%20study%20interactions%20between%20microplastics%20and%20immune%20cells%20in%20the%20walls%20of%20blood%20vessels.%20He%20hopes%20to%20expand%20this%20research%20beyond%20the%20carotid%20artery%20and%20also%20run%20some%20animal%20experiments%20to%20test%20for%20cause%20and%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlmost%20all%20of%20what%20we%20know%20about%20microplastics%20in%20the%20human%20body%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20look%2C%20can%20be%20summed%20up%20as%3A%20It's%20there%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20study%20further%20as%20to%20what%20it's%20doing%2C%20if%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroplastics-artery-plaque-mysterious-link-stroke-heart-attack-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745363215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ins