Park%20where%20a%20small%20group%20of%20lawyers%20wore%20masks%20out%20of%20concern%20for%20appearing%20in%20an%20online%20photo%20seen%20by%20their%20bosses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20who%20worked%20for%20nonprofits%20mused%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20their%20organization's%20tax-deductible%20status%20being%20subject%20to%20an%20audit.%20Another%20said%20his%20nonprofit%20moved%20its%20archives%20to%20a%20secure%20location%20offsite%20and%20encouraged%20other%20lawyers%20to%20think%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20their%20offices%20were%20raided%20by%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20among%20the%20rows%20and%20rows%20of%20lawyers%2C%20some%20hope%20broke%20through%20the%20anger%20and%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20good%20deal%20of%20gratitude%20directed%20towards%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20attitude%20in%20which%20we're%20living%20now%20is%20one%20of%20fear%20and%20intimidation%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20yet%20many%20judges%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bvery%20brave%2C%20very%20courageous%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scheindlin%2C%20the%20retired%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20you%20imagine%20if%20we%20did%20not%20have%20a%20judiciary%20right%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked%20from%20the%20dais.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20one%20of%20these%20executive%20orders%20would%20be%20carried%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaazel%20noted%20three%20reasons%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Broom%20for%20hope.%26quot%3B%20One%20was%20Harvard%20University's%20decision%20to%20sue%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20The%20second%20was%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20late-night%20order%20over%20the%20weekend%20barring%20further%20deportations%20under%20the%20Alien%20Enemies%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20reason%20for%20hope%3F%20A%20recent%20town%20hall%20held%20by%20Republican%20Sen.%20Chuck%20Grassley%20in%20Fort%20Madison%2C%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20all%20these%20folks%20in%20Iowa%20%E2%80%94%20these%20are%20not%2C%20you%20know