leagues%20and%20brands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20event%20started%2015%20years%20ago%20and%20has%20created%20a%20network%20of%20800%20to%20900%20women%20in%20sports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMembers%20said%20the%20network%20has%20led%20to%20job%20opportunities%2C%20mentorship%2C%20and%20women's%20sports%20initiatives.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20day%2C%20Elizabeth%20Lindsey%20at%20the%20agency%20Wasserman%20sends%20NFL%20chief%20revenue%20officer%20Renie%20Anderson%20a%20wine%20glass%20emoji.%20It%20means%20it's%20time%20to%20grab%20a%20drink%20and%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%20and%20Anderson%20are%20among%20a%20group%20of%20high-powered%20women%20sports%20leaders%20whose%20regular%20gatherings%20have%20become%20a%20source%20of%20dealmaking%2C%20career%20advancement%2C%20and%20support%20in%20their%20corner%20of%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20connection%20began%20growing%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20Lindsey%20brought%20together%20about%2010%20friends%20for%20drinks%20while%20they%20were%20in%20Miami%20for%20the%20CAA%20World%20Congress%20of%20Sports.%20Other%20women%20from%20the%20sports%20world%20spotted%20them%20at%20the%20bar%20and%20joined%20their%20conversation.%20They%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20an%20annual%20meetup%2C%20which%20Lindsey%20has%20helped%20organize%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20be%20a%20senior%20woman%20in%20this%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindsey%2C%20the%20global%20president%20of%20brands%20and%20properties%20for%20Wasserman%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20this%20gathering%20did%20for%20those%20women%20is%20give%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20an%20outlet%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year%20where%20you%20could%20breathe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%20estimates%20that%20the%20Women%20of%20Sports%20Cocktail%2C%20as%20the%20annual%20April%20event%20is%20now%20known%2C%20has%20grown%20to%20include%20a%20database%20of%20roughly%20800%20to%20900%20women%20across%20sports.%20It's%20helped%20connect%20them%20with%20jobs%20and%20mentorship%20and%20propel%20initiatives%20to%20grow%20women's%20sports.%20In%20addition%20to%20Lindsey%20and%20Anderson%2C%20participants%20have%20included%20former%20LA28%20Olympics%20CEO%20Kathy%20Carter%2C%20the%20US%20Tennis%20Association's%20commercial%20chief%20Kirsten%20Corio%2C%20and%20Kerry%20Tatlock%2C%20the%20National%20Basketball%20Association's%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20global%20partnerships%20and%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20one%20night%20a%20year%2C%20you're%20not%20the%20only%20woman%20in%20the%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindsey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258265ae0-ea81-4b90-a754-2cb43bba61fe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20the%20cocktail%20hour%20brings%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20and%20positions%20together%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20meetup%20has%20become%20a%20who's%20who%20of%20women%20leaders%20in%20sports%20and%20a%20key%20networking%20forum.%20Attendees%20are%20encouraged%20to%20bring%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20to%20expand%20the%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20more%20of%20us%20at%20the%20senior%20level%2C%20and%20I%20think%20there%20are%20more%20coming%20through%20the%20system%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Tatlock%20at%20the%20NBA%20said%20of%20the%20growth%20of%20women%20leaders%20across%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%2C%20Anderson%2C%20and%20Tatlock%20said%20this%20network%20has%20led%20to%20job%20opportunities.%20Anderson%20said%20she's%20personally%20hired%20a%20few%20women%20she%20met%20at%20the%20event.%C2%A0Lindsay%20said%20hiring%20managers%20who%20want%20to%20hire%20more%20women%20have%20contacted%20her%20for%20recommendations%20to%20fill%20roles%20like%20team%20presidents%2C%20athletic%20directors%2C%20or%20chief%20revenue%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20times%2C%20women%20come%20to%20Lindsey%2C%20who's%20become%20known%20for%20these%20events%2C%20simply%20to%20get%20an%20introduction%20to%20another%20exec.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20relationships%20are%20valuable%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20really%20positive%20stuff%20for%20someone%20willing%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20this%20network%20of%20women%20continued%20to%20connect%20over%20Zoom.%20They%20helped%20Mori%20Taheripour%2C%20an%20author%20with%20a%20sports%20business%20background%2C%20launch%20her%20book%20about%20negotiation%2C%20in%20one%20example%20of%20how%20they%20rallied%20around%20each%20other%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20meetings%20also%20inspired%20Wasserman%20to%20launch%20its%20women's%20sports%20research%20branch%2C%20The%20Collective%2C%20six%20years%20ago.%20Wasserman%20already%20represented%20athletes%2C%20executives%2C%20and%20other%20women%20in%20sports%2C%20and%20The%20Collective%20aimed%20to%20help%20others%20see%20the%20potential%20for%20the%20women's%20sports%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20thinking%20about%20how%20we%20take%20all%20of%20the%20resources%20that%20we%20have%20at%20Wasserman%2C%20how%20do%20we%20leverage%20some%20of%20those%20incredible%20executives%20to%20be%20smarter%20about%20women%20as%20consumers%20or%20as%20fans%20of%20women's%20sports%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Thayer%20Lavielle%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20The%20Collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20has%20also%20led%20to%20deal%20negotiations.%20Anderson%20and%20Lindsay%20said%20they've%20worked%20on%20sponsorship%20deals%20involving%20the%20NFL%20and%20brands%20like%20Nationwide%20and%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20deals%20together%2C%20and%20it's%2C%20and%20it's%20cool%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%20with%20someone%20that%20you%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%20said%20she's%20seen%20many%20women%20rise%20through%20the%20ranks%20from%20low-level%20managers%20to%20senior%20executives%20of%20m