nsider.com%2F68011736c6ad288d147e6d81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221411%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20and%20antitrust%20regulators%20are%20facing%20off%20in%20another%20court%20hearing.%3Cp%3EJakub%20Porzycki%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20judge%20will%20likely%20target%20Google's%20search%20deals%20with%20Apple%20to%20address%20its%20monopoly%2C%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20and%20the%20DOJ%20are%20facing%20off%20in%20a%20court%20hearing%20to%20determine%20remedies%20to%20its%20search%20monopoly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20proposed%20remedies%2C%20the%20DOJ%20wants%20the%20judge%20to%20force%20Google%20to%20sell%20off%20Chrome.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20will%20almost%20certainly%20target%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faapl-share-price-google-pays-apple-9-billion-annually-tac-goldman-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20multibillion%20dollar%20search%20engine%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Apple%20and%20other%20companies%20as%20part%20of%20a%20way%20to%20remedy%20the%20tech%20empire's%20illegal%20online%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-violated-antitrust-law-to-keep-search-monopoly-judge-rules-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esearch%20monopoly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20antitrust%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-case-chrome-android-sale-monopoly-doj-remedy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20began%20an%20expected%20three-week-long%20court%20battle%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20that%20could%20result%20in%20a%20massive%20shake%20up%20of%20the%20%241.8%20trillion%20tech%20behemoth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Amit%20Mehta%20will%20ultimately%20determine%20Google's%20fate%20following%20the%20so-called%20remedies%20phase%20of%20the%20landmark%20case.%20Mehta%20ruled%20in%20August%20that%20Google%20violated%20US%20antitrust%20law%20in%20maintaining%20a%20monopoly%20with%20its%20online%20search%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20DOJ%20gets%20its%20way%2C%20Google%20could%20be%20forced%20to%20sell%20off%20its%20key%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-sell-chrome-search-winners-losers-doj-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChrome%3C%2Fa%3E%20web%20browser%2C%20end%20its%20exclusive%20deals%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-share-price-trump-tariffs-valuation-sell-off-china-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ffirefox-extensions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMozilla%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Samsung%20and%20others%20to%20make%20Google%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20web%20browsers%20and%20smartphones%2C%20and%20share%20search%20data%20with%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ%20also%20wants%20the%20court%20to%20force%20Google%20to%20break%20off%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fandroid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E%20mobile%20operating%20system%20if%20the%20search%20market%20doesn't%20experience%20an%20increase%20in%20competition%20through%20its%20sweeping%20proposed%20fixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20in%20antitrust%20law%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Mehta%20will%20most%20likely%20rule%20for%20Google%20to%20end%20its%20multibillion%20dollar%20deals%20with%20companies%2C%20including%20Apple%2C%20to%20be%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20their%20devices%20and%20browsers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f824c3f4-d363-401f-818d-7475973ec014%5C%22%3EChrome%20sell%20off%20would%20be%20'worst%20case%20scenario'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20judge%20is%20almost%20certainly%20going%20to%20order%20Google%20to%20stop%20paying%20for%20exclusive%20default%20status%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rebecca%20Haw%20Allensworth%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20Tennessee's%20Vanderbilt%20University.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20know%20what%20exclusive%20default%20status%20means%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllensworth%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btoss%20up%26quot%3B%20on%20whether%20the%20judge%20will%20force%20Google%20to%20divest%20Chrome.%20Requiring%20Google%20to%20sell%20off%20Chrome%20would%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20case%20scenario%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20company%2C%20said%20Allensworth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDivestiture%20remedies%20are%20seen%20as%20pretty%20strong%20medicine%2C%26quot%3B%20Allensworth%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20break%20up%20remedy%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20very%20closely%20related%20to%20the%20behavior%20at%20issue%20in%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20what%2C%20Allensworth%20said%20she%20believes%20there%20will%20be%20what's%20called%20a%20behavioral%20remedy%20for%20Google%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20the%20judge%20will%20require%20Google%20to%20change%20how%20it%20arranges%20its%20contracts%20with%20distributors%20like%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20just%20don't%20know%20exactly%20how%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20designed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Allensworth%20said%20it%20would%20be%20very%20unlikely%20that%20the%20judge%20would%20order%20Google%20to%20divest%20both%20Chrome%20and%20Android.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202023%2C%20when%20the%20antitrust%20case%20went%20to%20trial%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20in%20court%20that%20in%202021%20Google%20paid%20companies%20more%20than%20%2426%20billion%20for%20the%20search%20placement%20deals.%20In%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-apple-iphone-search-engine-safari-deal-20-billion-2022-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20paid%20Apple%20a%20whopping%20%2420%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20secure%20itself%20as%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20the%20company's%20Safari%20browser%2C%20the%20DOJ%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20trial%2C%20the%20judge%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20deal%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20Google%20had%20paid%20Apple%20billions%2C%20%26quot%3Bsaying%20why%20would%20they%20do%20so%20if%20it%20didn't%20lock%20users%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20George%20Hay%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Cornell%20Law%20School%20and%20former%20chief%20economist%20for%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20antitrust%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20clearly%20believed%20that%20the%20payment%20had%20that%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20Hay%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20eliminating%20the%20agreement%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20most%20straightforward%20way%20to%20try%20to%20set%20things%20right.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20likely%20argue%20that's%20not%20enough%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20Reese%2C%20an%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20New%20York%20University%2C%20said%20that%20Google's%20exclusivity%20deals%20with%20Apple%20and%20other%20companies%20%26quot%3Bhave%20been%20close%20to%20the%20smoking%20gun%20for%20DOJ%20and%20other%20critics%20because%20they%20allegedly%20show%20naked%20attempts%20to%20control%20the%20market%20and%20neutralize%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReese%20noted%20the%20DOJ%20%26quot%3Bwent%20big%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20remedies%20that%20it%20is%20seeking%20for%20Google%2C%20but%20said%20that%20getting%20them%20all%20would%20probably%20%26quot%3Bsurprise%26quot%3B%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20stop%20short%20of%20saying%20we%20will%20see%20every%20remedy%20sought%20by%20DOJ%20ordered%2C%20but%20I%20do%20believe%20it%20will%20be%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHay%20told%20BI%20that%20by%20asking%20the%20judge%20for%20as%20much%20as%20it%20did%2C%20the%20DOJ%20is%20%26quot%3Binviting%20Google%20to%20confirm%20that%20something%20less%20draconian%20will%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20of%20course%20says%20it%20wants%20almost%20no%20remedy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20is%20expected%20to%20issue%20his%20remedies%20ruling%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summer.%20Google%20has%20vowed%20to%20appeal%20Mehta's%20ruling%20in%20which%20he%20declared%20the%20tech%20giant%20a%20monopolist.%20It%20could%20be%20years%20before%20there's%20a%20final%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESyracuse%20University%20law%20professor%20Shubha%20Ghosh%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20more%20drastic%20a%20remedy%20that%20gets%20imposed%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20more%20likely%20it'll%20get%20reversed%20on%20appeal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e07938d-0ae1-48de-b8e4-f5243596bde2%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20lawyer%20called%20DOJ's%20proposal%20a%20'wish%20list'%20for%20rivals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20opening%20statement%20on%20Monday%2C%20Google%20lawyer%20John%20Schmidtlein%20called%20the%20DOJ's%20proposal%20of%20remedies%20%26quot%3Ba%20wish%20list%20for%20competitors%20looking%20to%20get%20the%20benefits%20of%20Google's%20extraordinary%20innovations%20and%20trade%20secrets%20that%20we've%20spent%20decades%20developing%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F04%2F21%2Ftechnology%2Fgoogle-search-remedies-hearing.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20vice%20president%20for%20regulatory%20affairs%20Lee-Anne%20Mulholland%20said%20the%20government's%20proposal%20was%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%20and%20harmful%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ's%20proposal%20would%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20people%20to%20use%20Google%20search%2C%20%26quot%3Bjeopardize%26quot%3B%20users'%20privacy%20and%20security%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bhamstring%26quot%3B%20how%20the%20company%20develops%20AI%2C%20Mulholland%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustice%20Department%20lawyer%20David%20Dahlquist%20said%20in%20his%20opening%20statement%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20court%20must%20prevent%20Google%20from%20using%20its%20search%20monopoly%20to%20dominate%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-companies-squeezed-by-ai-alixpartners-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20AI%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court's%20remedy%20should%20be%20forward%20looking%20and%20not%20ignore%20what's%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%26quot%3B%20Dahlquist%20said%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20is%20using%20the%20same%20strategy%20that%20they%20did%20for%20search%20and%20now%20applying%20it%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flatest-google-gemini-2-5-flash-has-thinking-budget-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGemini%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20lawyer%20argued%20that%20Gemini%20rival%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20doing%20just%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-billion-dollar-deal-apple-at-risk-monopoly-search-case-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745348819000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6807e11ca466d2b74ab3d4b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-billion-dollar-deal-apple-at-risk-monopoly-search-case-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20federal%20judge%20will%20ultimately%20determine%20Google's%20fate%20after%20he%20ruled%20that%20the%20tech%20giant%20holds%20an%20illegal%20online%20search