%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20loved%20how%20secluded%20and%20connected%20with%20nature%20the%20place%20was.%20And%20people%20who%20knew%20us%20understood%20that%20this%20is%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20place%20we%20would%20invest%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Sylvia.%20It%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20decision%20to%20change%20a%20barren%20land%20into%20a%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20surprising%20part%3F%20They%20never%20intended%20to%20start%20a%20homestay%20at%20all.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20wanted%20the%20place%20for%20personal%20use.%20But%20we%20had%20to%20do%20it%20because%20we%20had%20to%20sustain%20it%2C%20and%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20keep%20it%20as%20a%20second%20home%20or%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20keep%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20dreams%20brick%20by%20brick%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sylvia%20and%20John%20first%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20patch%20of%20forest%20that%20would%20one%20day%20become%20Off%20The%20Grid%2C%20it%20was%20little%20more%20than%20a%20dream.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F411488%2Fzero-waste-homes-future-sustainability-reduce-carbon-footprint-eco-friendly-alternatives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20road%2C%20no%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20even%20a%20real%20path.%20Just%20this%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20stillness%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sylvia%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20stillness%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deter%20them.%20Over%20the%20next%20four%20years%2C%20they%20built%20slowly%2C%20painstakingly%2C%20adding%20one%20structure%20at%20a%20time%20during%20the%20dry%20seasons.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20a%20few%20years%20because%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20year%20from%202006%2C%20we%20just%20did%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20heavy%20rain%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20cut%20off%20by%20rivers%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20So%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20in%20and%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sylvia%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20access%20was%20a%20challenge%20in%20itself.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20like%20a%20riverbed%20for%2010%20kilometres%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sylvia%20says.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20could%20either%20walk%20it%20or%20go%20on%20a%20four-wheeler%2C%20a%20tractor%2C%20or%20a%20bike.%E2%80%9D%20On%20one%20occasion%2C%20their%20tractor%20lost%20balance%20and%20toppled%20over%20on%20the%20muddy%20track.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20carry%20all%20the%20bricks%20for%20the%20main%20house%20for%20the%20last%20two%20kilometres%20or%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20humour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelp%20from%20the%20local%20hands%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20homestay%20came%20to%20life%20not%20through%20contractors%20or%20architects%2C%20but%20through%20the%20hands%20of%20villagers%20from%20a%20tiny%20hamlet%20of%20just%20fifteen%20houses%20nearby.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20village%20kind%20of%20works%20as%20a%20community.%20They%20get%20together%20and%20build%20one%20person%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20and%20when%20the%20next%20person%20is%20building%2C%20everyone%20chips%20in%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccustomed%20to%20forest%20life%20and%20deeply%20skilled%20in%20traditional%20craftsmanship%20%E2%80%94%20from%20digging%20wells%20to%20carving%20wood%20%E2%80%94%20these%20villagers%20became%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20build.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20great%20at%20working%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20very%20strong.%20One%20or%20two%20masons%20will%20always%20be%20there%20in%20these%20i